  "guidelines": "For French Instagram captions, adopt a friendly yet slightly formal tone. Avoid overly slangy expressions; keep language clear and elegant. Prefer short sentences and limit emojis to one or two. Maximum character count for standard posts is 80 characters (including spaces). Use the metric system and French punctuation (e.g., spaces before ‘:’, ‘;’, ‘!’)."
}

